         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translations</head>
            <div type="translation" source="#jmr-jbwp-rgg2003" xml:lang="en"><p> Property of the holy Menas. Lord God help <supplied reason="subaudible">us</supplied></p></div>
            </div>
       
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>This appears to define ecclesiastical property, presumably belonging to a church or monastery dedicated to Saint Menas. 
               This is the first evvidence for his cult in Cyrenaica</p>
            <p>For territorial disputes between Christian institutions Dobias-Lalou cites Synesios, Ep.66, l.216.</p>
         </div>
         
